Flume is a fast, modern, terminal-based IRC client built in Rust.

Features include multi-server connections, a rich TUI with theming and
split views, vi/emacs keybinding modes, Lua and Python scripting,
LLM-powered script and theme generation, DCC file transfers, XDCC,
emoji shortcodes, configurable display formats, and encrypted vault
for credentials.

WWW: https://github.com/FlumeIRC/flume
